(PID.TID 0001.0001) ># ===============================================================
(PID.TID 0001.0001) ># Vortex Sphere MITgcm Reference Case (MITgcm native solve)
(PID.TID 0001.0001) ># One-layer, global lat-lon, linearized barotropic dynamics.
(PID.TID 0001.0001) ># ===============================================================
(PID.TID 0001.0001) >
